data.description:
This stunning single-family home is located at 4902 Tidal Walk Dr, Beaufort, SC 29907. With a generous bed count of 5 and 3 full bathrooms, this spacious sanctuary is perfect for a growing family. Boasting a square footage of 2,421, this meticulously maintained property offers ample space for comfortable living. The home is adorned with upgrades throughout, including charming barn doors and a stylish shiplap kitchen island. Situated near a serene community pond, residents can enjoy peaceful views and a tranquil atmosphere. Additionally, the garage door screen adds convenience and versatility to the property. Don't miss the opportunity to call this extraordinary rental property your home!

Smoking allowed:No
